{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_lao_ren","text":"鹰记商号里那些蜡人是怎么来的？","tone":"沉声","chapter":58,"line_start":8,"line_end":10},{"speaker":"char_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"不知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":58,"line_start":12,"line_end":12},{"speaker":"char_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"我真的不知道。昨天早上鹰记商号一开门，那些蜡人就在那里了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":58,"line_start":16,"line_end":17},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_lao_ren","text":"鹰记商号的伙计呢？","tone":"陈述","chapter":58,"line_start":22,"line_end":22},{"speaker":"char_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"不知道。从昨天早上我就没有看到他们。","tone":"陈述","chapter":58,"line_start":24,"line_end":24},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_lao_ren","text":"连一个都没有看见？","tone":"疑问","chapter":58,"line_start":25,"line_end":26},{"speaker":"char_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"一个都没有。","tone":"陈述","chapter":58,"line_start":28,"line_end":28},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_lao_ren","text":"从昨天早上起，鹰记商号里就只有那几个蜡人在店里？连一个活人都没有？","tone":"疑问","chapter":58,"line_start":30,"line_end":32},{"speaker":"char_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"没有。绝对没有。","tone":"陈述","chapter":58,"line_start":34,"line_end":34},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_lao_ren","text":"你的意思是不是说，从昨天早上到现在，就只有这几个蜡人留在鹰记商号里？","tone":"疑问","chapter":58,"line_start":44,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"大概是这样子的。因为从昨天早上到现在，除了这几个蜡人外，谁也没有看见鹰记商号里有活人走动过。","tone":"陈述","chapter":58,"line_start":48,"line_end":51},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_lao_ren","text":"你知不知道鹰记商号经常都有很多值钱的货物？","tone":"陈述","chapter":58,"line_start":54,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"我知道。大家都知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":58,"line_start":56,"line_end":56},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_lao_ren","text":"店里既然只有这几个蜡人留守，难道就没有人打店里那些货物的主意？","tone":"疑问","chapter":58,"line_start":58,"line_end":59},{"speaker":"char_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"有过。从昨天早上到现在，至少已经有过五六拨人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":58,"line_start":62,"line_end":63},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_lao_ren","text":"那些人呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":58,"line_start":66,"line_end":66},{"speaker":"char_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"全都死了。一走进鹰记的大门就死了。","tone":"恐惧","chapter":58,"line_start":68,"line_end":68},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_lao_ren","text":"只要一走进大门就死？不管什么人都一样？","tone":"疑问","chapter":58,"line_start":70,"line_end":70},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":null,"text":"那些人是怎么死的？他们的尸体在哪里？","tone":"疑问","chapter":58,"line_start":76,"line_end":78}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_lao_ren","name":"老人","alias":[],"identity":"鹰记商号附近的知情老人","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"目睹鹰记商号蜡人异变的目击者","personality":{"traits":["胆小","诚实","谨慎","衰老","紧张"],"speech_style":"朴实直白","temperament":"怯懦"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[58],"source_refs":[{"chapter":58,"line_start":4,"line_end":6,"text":"老人的额角上已经痛出了冷汗"}]},{"id":"char_lao_da","name":"老大","alias":[],"identity":"五兄弟之首，据说能将人打成肉泥","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"五兄弟中的领袖，从不杀人只将人打成肉泥","personality":{"traits":["粗犷","豪迈","霸道","狡猾","护短"],"speech_style":"粗俗豪放","temperament":"暴烈"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_lao_er","type":"挚友","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"兄弟"},{"target":"char_lao_san","type":"挚友","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"兄弟"},{"target":"char_lao_si","type":"挚友","intensity":80,"bon